											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="~The player is walking toward the steps to the exterior courtyard of the monastery, just across the entrance bridge&#xD;&#xA;~They stop, hearing voices the player crouches by corner of an archway&#xD;&#xA;~Peering around they see a gith guard hustling three cultists to their feet. The cultists are prisoners, terrified of the guards." />
